title: Stephen Joseph, Medium Recycled Gift Bag with Handles, Kids, Reusable, Birthday Party Gift Bag, Shopping Bag
description: Party like there is no tomorrow with these colorful recycled medium gift bags. Not just a great way to package a gift, they are keeping the planet green. Each of our gift bags feature a bright, cheery design printed front and back. Double handles make the bag extra sturdy so that the special gift is safe inside. These bags are a great way to gift one of our many products to a special someone.
